Annabel Scholey https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Annabel_Scholey 0 Annabel Scholey (born 8 January 1984) is an English actress. She played Lauren Drake in the BBC supernatural drama Being Human (2009) and the leading role of 'Maddie' in the musical feature film Walking on Sunshine (2014). Scholey played Contessina de Medici in the television series, Medici: Masters of Florence with Dustin Hoffman and Richard Madden (2016).
